:: Intro {"position":"900,300","size":"100,100"}
You are a monster hunter, intent on destroying the beasts who killed your family. However, you face the Orda Aldressia, who have sided with the monsters. Specifically, they have sent a task force led by the elite detective and battlemage, Valen. In order to continue your pursuit of justice, they must be destroyed.

