:: Retreat {"position":"700,500","size":"100,100"}
Before you engage, you notice the telltale signs of a trap. Coupled with gnolls not living in forests, like, at all, you find it prudent to leave. On your way home, you find a cornerstone of a Binding Circle, engraved with "Orda Aldressia, Silas Task Force."

Whoever these guys are, they are after you, and clearly very powerful.

[[Retreat(Inv)]]


